
Evoker

Focus: Conjuring based magic, pole combat, defense

Roleplay: Evokers are one of the common mage types found in most
cities. They are more focused on using magic to conjure effects, some
of which can be deadly. Their skills are mostly combat based, providing
the evoker with defense against multiple weapon types. They can be
found in most places where magic is practiced, such as libraries.

Difficulty: Moderate

